### ====================== 评价模块 ReviewController ======================
### 1. 提交评价（POST）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/review
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": 1,
  "userId": 1,
  "targetUserId": 2,
  "type": "RUNNER_REVIEW",
  "rating": 5,
  "content": "配送速度很快，服务很好"
}

### 2. 查询评价详情（GET）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/review/1
Accept: application/json

### 3. 查询某订单的评价列表（GET）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/review/order/1
Accept: application/json

### 4. 分页查询某用户的评价列表（GET）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/review/user/1?page=1&size=10&type=RUNNER_REVIEW
Accept: application/json

### 5. 查询用户评分统计（GET）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/review/user/1/rating-stats
Accept: application/json


### ====================== 订单模块 OrderController ======================
### 6. 发布订单（POST）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/order
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "publisherId": 1,
  "pickupAddress": "菜鸟驿站",
  "deliveryAddress": "学生宿舍1号楼",
  "reward": 5,
  "remark": "轻拿轻放"
}

### 7. 查询订单详情（GET）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/order/1
Accept: application/json

### 8. 分页查询订单列表（GET，支持筛选）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/order?page=1&size=10&status=PENDING&publisherId=1
Accept: application/json

### 9. 跑腿员接单（PUT）
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/order/1/accept
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "runnerId": 2
}

### 10. 开始配送（PUT）
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/order/1/deliver
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "runnerId": 2
}

### 11. 完成订单（PUT）
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/order/1/complete
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "runnerId": 2
}

### 12. 取消订单（PUT）
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/order/1/cancel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "reason": "临时有事不需要了"
}


### ====================== 跑腿员模块 RunnerController ======================
### 13. 跑腿员申请（POST）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/runner/apply
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 2,
  "name": "张三",
  "studentId": "2024001001",
  "phone": "13800138000"
}